sources.modules/header/header.sass:
//header-----------------------------------------	
.header_style
	background-color: #FFFFFF
	width: 100%
	height: 70px
	box-shadow: 0px 10px 20px rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.05)
	display: flex
	flex-direction: row
	align-items: center
	justify-content: space-between
//------------------------------------------------------



//–õ–æ–≥–æ—Ç–∏–ø------------------------------------------------
.header-logo
	margin: 15px 0px 15px 90px
//-------------------------------------------------------



//–ì–æ—Ä–∏–∑–æ–Ω—Ç–∞–ª—å–Ω–æ–µ –º–µ–Ω—é —Å—Å—ã–ª–æ–∫------------------------------
.header-menu 
	min-width: 450px
	width: 527px
	display: flex
	justify-content: space-between
	margin: 26px 0 26px 300px
	font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif
	font-size: 14px
	line-height: 17px
	color: rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.5)

.header-menu__item_home
	font-weight: bold

.header-menu__item_services-icon
	padding-left: 3px

nav.header-menu a, div.header-buttons a
	text-decoration: none 
	color: rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.5)

a:active
	color: rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.75)
//---------------------------------------------------------



//–í—Ö–æ–¥, —Ä–µ–≥–∏—Å—Ç—Ä–∞—Ü–∏—è----------------------------------------
.header-buttons
	min-width: 180px
	width: 200px
	margin: auto auto auto 25px
	font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif
	font-style: normal
	font-weight: bold
	font-size: 12px
	line-height: 15px
	display: flex
	justify-content: space-between

.header-buttons__login
	padding: 9px 20px 10px 20px
	border: 2px solid #BC9CFF
	border-radius: 22px
	color: #BC9CFF
	
.header-buttons__register
	padding: 9px 20px 10px 20px
	border: 2px solid #BC9CFF
	border-radius: 22px
	color: #FFFFFF
	background: linear-gradient(180deg, #BC9CFF 0%, #8BA4F9 100%)
//---------------------------------------------------------------------
sources.modules/login/login.sass:
//–°—Ç–∏–ª—å —Ñ–æ—Ä–º—ã –∏ —Ä–∞—Å–ø–æ–ª–æ–∂–µ–Ω–∏–µ —ç–ª–µ–º–µ–Ω—Ç–æ–≤ –≤ –Ω–µ–π-------------------------------------
.login-form
	width: 380px
	height: 358px
	left: 560px
	top: 701px
	background: #FFFFFF
	border: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12)
	box-sizing: border-box
	box-shadow: 0px 0px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2)
	border-radius: 4px

.login-form_wrap
	display: flex
	justify-content: flex start
	align-content: flex-start
	flex-flow: column nowrap
	width: 320px
	height: 300px
	margin: 25px 30px
	padding: 0px
//-------------------------------------------------------------------




//–ó–∞–≥–æ–ª–æ–≤–æ–∫-----------------------------------------------------------	
.login-form__header
	font-family: 'Quicksand', sans-serif
	font-weight: bold
	font-size: 24px
	line-height: 30px
	color: #1F2041
	width: 320px
	height: 30px
	margin-top: 10px
//--------------------------------------------------------------------




//–ü–æ–ª—è –≤–≤–æ–¥–∞----------------------------------------------------------
.login_input
	display: flex
	flex-flow: column nowrap

.login__email, .login__password
	border: none 
	outline: none 
	-webkit-appearance: none 
	border: 1px solid rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.25)
	box-sizing: border-box
	border-radius: 4px
	margin: 5px 0px
	width: 320px
	height: 44px
	font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif
	font-size: 14px
	line-height: 18px
	color: rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.25)
	padding-left: 15px
//--------------------------------------------------------------------




//–í—Ö–æ–¥ –≤ –ø—Ä–æ—Ñ–∏–ª—å--------------------------------------------------------
.login-form_enter
	display: flex
	flex-flow: row noform
	position: relative

.login__button
	border: none 
	outline: none 
	-webkit-appearance: none 
	background: linear-gradient(180deg, #BC9CFF 0%, #8BA4F9 100%)
	border-radius: 22px
	width: 100%
	height: 42px
	margin-top: 15px
	font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif
	font-style: normal
	font-weight: bold
	font-size: 12px
	line-height: 15px
	text-align: center
	text-transform: uppercase
	color: #FFFFFF
	cursor: pointer

.login__button-img
	position: absolute
	top: 47%
	right: 3%
//-------------------------------------------------------------------------




//–ö–Ω–æ–ø–∫–∞ —Å–æ–∑–¥–∞–Ω–∏—è –ø—Ä–æ—Ñ–∏–ª—è –∏ —Ç–µ–∫—Å—Ç------------------------------------------
.login-form_create
	margin-top: 25px
	display: flex
	justify-content: space-between
	align-items: center

.create__text
	font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif
	font-size: 14px
	line-height: 18px

.login__create
	background-color: #FFFFFF
	border: none 
	outline: none 
	-webkit-appearance: none 
	font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif
	font-weight: bold
	font-size: 12px
	line-height: 15px
	text-align: center
	text-transform: uppercase
	padding: 13px 24px
	border: 2px solid #BC9CFF
	border-radius: 22px
	color: #BC9CFF
	cursor: pointer
//-------------------------------------------------------------------------

//–∫–æ–Ω—Ç–µ–π–Ω–µ—Ä —ç–ª–µ–º–µ–Ω—Ç–æ–≤ about----------------------------
.about_style
	background: #FFFFFF
	box-shadow: 0px 1px 0px rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.1)
	display: flex
	align-items: center
	justify-content: space-around
	height: 372px
//------------------------------------------------------



//–õ–æ–≥–æ—Ç–∏–ø —Å —Ç–µ–∫—Å—Ç–æ–º---------------------------
.logo_style
	width: 260px
	height: 156px
	display: flex
	align-content: center
	justify-content: flex-start
	flex-direction: column
	font-family: Montserrat
	font-style: normal
	font-weight: normal
	font-size: 14px
	line-height: 24px
	color: rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.75)

.about-logo__text
	line-height: 24px
//----------------------------------------------



//–ú–µ–Ω—é —Å–æ —Å—Å—ã–ª–∫–∞–º–∏-------------------------------
.about-menu
	width: 800px
	display: flex
	align-content: flex-start
	justify-content: space-between
	height: 170px

.about-links
	display: flex
	flex-flow: column nowrap
	justify-content: flex-start
	align-items: flex-start
	
div.about-menu a,span,h3,p
	font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif
	font-size: 14px
	line-height: 40px
	color: rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.5)
	text-decoration: none

.about-links__header
	font-size: 12px
	font-weight: bold
	text-transform: uppercase
	color: #1F2041
//------------------------------------------------



//–ë–ª–æ–∫ –æ—Ç–ø—Ä–∞–≤–∫–∏ EMAIL-------------------------------
.form__subscrime_style
	display: flex
	flex-direction: column
	align-content: flex-start
	justify-content: flex-start
	width: 250px
	height: 84p—Ö

h3.sub-content__header
	font-size: 12px
	text-transform: uppercase
	color: #1F2041

p.sub-content__text
	line-height: 200%
	padding-bottom: 16px
	
.subscribe__input
	border: 1px solid rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.25) 
	border-radius: 4px
	display: flex
	flex-flow: row nowrap
	justify-content: space-between
	padding: 10px
   
input.sub__input-email
	border: none 
	outline: none 
	-webkit-appearance: none 
	width: 274px 
	vertical-align: center 
	font-size: 14px
	color: rgba(31, 32, 65, 0.25)
   
input.sub__input-submit
	width: 20px 
	height: 20px 
	border: none 
	background: url(/modules/about/img/forward.png) no-repeat 95% 95%
	align: center
//------------------------------------------------------------------------
